q.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9e9" alt="" class="close-faq" /></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9ea" class="div-answer"><div class="feature-faq-rich-block w-richtext"><p>Most experts will give you this advice - “Just start writing! Seriously, the hardest part about writing is getting started. Once you get going, the words will start flowing and before you know it, you&#x27;ll have a whole article.”</p><p>We believe in the same, but to get started you need some help. If you&#x27;re having trouble starting an article, use Writesonic’s AI Article writing features to get your creative juices flowing.</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9ed" class="block-question"><div class="div-question mob-mb-12"><h3 class="question">How do I write a good article?</h3><div class="div-open-question"><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e62bea45c9cf_down-faq.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="open-faq" /><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e6fd6245c9ce_orange-plus.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9f3" alt="" class="orange-plus-faq" /><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e615b245c9d0_up-faq.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9f4" alt="" class="close-faq" /></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9f5" class="div-answer"><div class="feature-faq-rich-block w-richtext"><p>The usual and long way of writing a good article is: First and foremost, start by choosing a topic that you&#x27;re passionate about. If you&#x27;re not interested in the topic, it will be very difficult to write a good article about it.</p><p>Once you&#x27;ve chosen your topic, do some research and make sure you have a good understanding of it. This will make it easier to write about and will also help you to avoid making any mistakes. Once you feel confident that you know what you&#x27;re talking about, it&#x27;s time to start writing.</p><p>Try to keep your article concise and to the point. It&#x27;s important to be clear and concise in your writing, as this will help to keep your readers engaged. It&#x27;s also a good idea to proofread your article before you publish it, to make sure there are no errors.</p><p>The above-mentioned way also takes hours of your time and immense hardwork. Want to know a hack? Write with Writesonic! Here all you need is a topic in mind to start and Writesonic’s Instant Article Writer will create high-quality content for you in seconds.</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9f8" class="block-question"><div class="div-question mob-mb-12"><h3 class="question">How long does it take to write a 1000-word article?</h3><div class="div-open-question"><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e62bea45c9cf_down-faq.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" width="24" class="open-faq" /><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e6fd6245c9ce_orange-plus.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9fe" alt="" class="orange-plus-faq" /><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e615b245c9d0_up-faq.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958e9ff" alt="" class="close-faq" /></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958ea00" class="div-answer"><div class="feature-faq-rich-block w-richtext"><p>If you&#x27;re a fast typist, it might take you around two hours to write a 1000-word article. But if you&#x27;re a slower typist, it might take you closer to three hours.</p><p>Assuming you&#x27;re a fast typist, let&#x27;s say you can type 100 words in 10 minutes. That means you could write a 1000-word article in 100 minutes, or 1 hour and 40 minutes.</p><p>But that&#x27;s not all! You also have to factor in things like breaks, research, and editing. So the whole process might take you closer to 3 hours. But of course, this all depends on how fast you type, how much research you need to do, and how much editing you need to do. So it really varies from person to person.</p><p>However, Writesonic’s AI writing tools can make the job faster and easier. With just a topic, you can write an entire 1000-word article in seconds.</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958ea03" class="block-question"><div class="div-question mob-mb-12"><h3 class="question">How quickly can you write an article?</h3><div class="div-open-question"><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e62bea45c9cf_down-faq.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="open-faq" /><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e6fd6245c9ce_orange-plus.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958ea09" alt="" class="orange-plus-faq" /><img src="https://global-uploads.webflow.com/627a1044a798e6627445c8d1/627a1045a798e615b245c9d0_up-faq.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958ea0a" alt="" class="close-faq" /></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958ea0b" class="div-answer"><div class="feature-faq-rich-block w-richtext"><p>Normally, the answer to this question depends on the person asking it, and the person&#x27;s level of expertise in writing. For someone who is just starting out, it may take a while to write an article. However, for someone who is a seasoned professional, it may only take a few minutes.</p><p>But, with an AI article writing tool, anyone can write articles and blog posts in seconds. Try creating one with Writesonic’s Instant Article Writer for free now!</p></div></div></div><div data-w-id="7d716a68-cb07-fd3b-cdd1-aee36958ea0e" class="block-question"><div class="div-question mob-mb-12"><h3 class="question">How long does it take to